{"id":231784070,"title":"早上不生氣 還醒腦的好物...","content":"芝加哥 ＃Top 3 ＃連鎖咖啡\n\n每天早上來一杯美式醒腦，我自己喜歡苦而不酸ㄉ，而以下將分享我最常喝的連鎖咖啡店 top 3啦！！！\n（這些咖啡天店在loop可說是到處都是，所以非常方便～）\n\n＃Top 1 la colombe (五星好評)\n美式夠味，偏苦味，所以我非常喜歡\n但！！！最好喝的是Iced draft latte ！！！\n我就會平日喝美式，假日喝draft latte \n（他們有販賣罐裝的咖啡，但拿鐵類的都偏甜，但比starbucks罐裝好喝很多）\nhttps://i.imgur.com/sv4TI7j.jpg\n \nhttps://i.imgur.com/OGjpciE.jpg\n＃Top 2 intelligentsia \n美式夠味，偏酸味，但是是苦味人可以接受的酸\n這家拿鐵比美式好喝喔～有neighborhood discount，住附近可以跟店員說會打折\nhttps://i.imgur.com/ayhZ45o.jpg\n\n#Top 3 Starbucks\nStarbucks到處都有，但小瞥步是下載starbucks app集星星\n集一集有不少免費咖啡喝呢！！！\n那starbucks就來推薦一點咖啡以外的飲料好了\nGreen tea latte / 喝起來就是抹茶，完全沒咖啡味，當在美國懷念抹茶味，就要喝這ㄧ味！！！\nDragonfruit mango tea（不要加lemonade/ 夏天喝起來就是好喝的色素水，冰冰涼涼有淡淡清香的火龍果茶味\nhttps://i.imgur.com/tEr06pN.jpg\n\n（而芝加哥藝術學院樓下有pret很方便，有學生discount，不過美式咖啡喝起來跟水ㄧ樣...） \n以上","excerpt":"芝加哥 ＃Top 3 ＃連鎖咖啡，每天早上來一杯美式醒腦，我自己喜歡苦而不酸ㄉ，而以下將分享我最常喝的連鎖咖啡店 top 3啦！！！，（這些咖啡天店在loop可說是到處都是，所以非常方便～），＃Top","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-02T18:24:18.595Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-02T18:24:18.595Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":24,"tags":[],"topics":["食物","咖啡","咖啡廳","學校","日常"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"芝加哥藝術學院","department":"還在摸索","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":24}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/sv4TI7j.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/OGjpciE.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/ayhZ45o.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/tEr06pN.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"2736d1c1-72a0-4b3f-a6d2-c1b2e9c7a8f3","url":"https://i.imgur.com/sv4TI7j.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/sv4TI7j.jpg"